        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for work sent by GdeS and A. F. Marion [<hi rend="italic">L’évolution du règne végétal</hi> 1 (1881)]. CD greatly pleased at boldness with which GdeS expresses his belief in evolution. Some of GdeS’s countrymen have been "a little timid" on this head.</p> 
